                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">A reincarnate line of spells for all int casters would be a nice direction to take.
<br />

<br />
Reincarnation differs from rez in such a way that there is a chance you will not come back as the same being you died as....ie  a male human dies and is reincarnated as a female dark elf.
<br />

<br />
Each int caster would have their specialties:  mages could also bring you back as an elemental...necrose could bring you back as any number of undead types...chanters -- just pick one of their illusion types.
<br />

<br />
As an added bonus...one type of mob in each zone could be used(gets tricky here most mobs aren't universal so you would die on leaving said zone)  
<br />

<br />
Remember, Reincarnation is a roll of the dice so should the exp regained.
<br />

<br />
The new form lasts as long as you live except for the special type which dies on leaving said zone.
<br />

<br />
Wisdom casters should really be given rez earlier than level 70.  Shamans and druids should have rez similar to palis.  Bst and rangers much later of course.
<br />

<br />
To help the clerics feel like they are still needed after these changes... they receive the hold line of spells...any three mobs can be held(immobilized) for 4 ticks + 1 tick per lvl.  Casting time very quick -- recast say 5 ticks.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
        </tr>
