                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">This whole thread seems a liiiiittle bit strange to me.   Why would someone -want- a reincarnate again?  Hell, you already have people whining about paladin rezzes, for crying out loud (oh noz! I am losing 0.36% of a level! (Do the math. 1 death at 70 = ~6% XP loss. %6 (the difference between paladin and cleric rezzes) of %6 = 0.36%.))  Why would someone accept some wonky "my ogre warrior is now a gnome and lost his immunity to frontal stun and oh, dangit, only wound up with a 50% "rez"" reincarnation thing.
<br />

